♫ In my heart. One-step, two-step, let's dance ♫

308
00:23:14,470 --> 00:23:18,700
♫ As our gaze follows the fingers, our feelings are mutual ♫

309
00:23:18,700 --> 00:23:24,330
♫ The feelings that cannot be put into words are precious ♫

310
00:23:24,330 --> 00:23:29,100
♫ If the sky is clear tomorrow, ♫

311
00:23:29,100 --> 00:23:34,570
♫ Will you smile? ♫

312
00:23:34,570 --> 00:23:39,480
♫ Darling, for you, love is simple ♫

313
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:44,950
♫ Darling, I need you. Coming anytime, anytime ♫

