00:23:48,836 --> 00:23:51,466
I want Takara to be happy.

317
00:23:51,466 --> 00:23:53,676
No one would ever hate that guy for real.

318
00:23:53,676 --> 00:23:56,866
It's okay. I'll treat Amagi well.

